  "identifier": "HB 648",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to motor vehicle dealers.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 190.046 to establish conditions for reimbursement of motor vehicle dealers by manufacturers, component manufacturers, and distributors for parts and warranty or recall work on motor vehicles with a classification of 7 or higher as established in 49 C.F.R. sec. 565.15; define \"component manufacturer\"; expand the time frame for a dealer to submit a claim for warranty work from 30 days to 90 days.",
